# SPA Routing Rules for Tamuu (Improved for Asset Security)
# Ensures that missing assets return 404 instead of index.html (fixing SyntaxError: Unexpected token <)

# 1. ASSET GUARD (Prevent JS/CSS 404s from returning HTML index)
/assets/*  /assets/:splat  404
/images/*  /images/:splat  404

# 2. SPA CATCH-ALL
/*  /index.html  200
